                behavioral patterns and mental health conditions associated with
                alcoholism. According to the National Institute on Alcohol Abuse
                and Alcoholism (NIAAA), structured therapeutic approaches and
                medications like naltrexone can significantly aid in recovery.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
